dns resolving library for XIP enabled dns server

nameserver list to be stored in /etc/resolv.xiaconf
	sample /etc/resolv.xiaconf
	--------
	# xia resolving server list					<-- comment starting with #
	nameserver 127.0.0.1						<-- nameserver
	--------

host list to be stored in /etc/hosts_xia
	smaple /etc/host_xia
	--------
	# xia host list								<-- comment starting with #
	sample.com RE AD:### HID:### SID:###		<-- DAG followed by domain name
	--------
note that /etc/host_xia format is different from original /etc/host
in the domain name comes before DAG
(for simplicity in parsing, since DAG contains white space)

